11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_MIXER_DEFAULT_OUTPUT_RATE_CALCULATOR_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_MIXER_DEFAULT_OUTPUT_RATE_CALCULATOR_H_
13
14#include <vector>
15
16#include "api/array_view.h"
17#include "modules/audio_mixer/output_rate_calculator.h"
18
19namespace webrtc {
20
21class DefaultOutputRateCalculator : public OutputRateCalculator {
22 public:
23 static const int kDefaultFrequency = 48000;
24
25 // Produces the least native rate greater or equal to the preferred
26 // sample rates. A native rate is one in
27 // AudioProcessing::NativeRate. If |preferred_sample_rates| is
28 // empty, returns |kDefaultFrequency|.
29 int CalculateOutputRateFromRange(
30 rtc::ArrayView<const int> preferred_sample_rates) override;
31 ~DefaultOutputRateCalculator() override {}
32};
33
34} // namespace webrtc
35
36#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_MIXER_DEFAULT_OUTPUT_RATE_CALCULATOR_H_
